  "description": "Product Description Firm &amp; renew your skin with our Polypeptide Facial Serum. Packed with 3 Peptides, Rice Protein and Lavender oil, our plumping formula helps improve moisture balance and the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles, promoting a healthier-looking complexion. Apply morning and evening for an extra dewy glow! Vegan Friendly. Ingredients Unsweetened Cocoa, Sugar, Cocoa Butter, Dietary fibre (Inulin &amp; Oligofructose, Dextrin), Flax Seeds (6%), Puffed Rice, Emulsifier: Soy Lecithin (GMO Free), Natural Vanilla. Cocoa Solids: 65% Minimum. Contains Soy Lecithin And Gluten. Directions Can be used either morning or evening. In the morning, apply a few drops of the serum directly on to the face before applying makeup. Gently massage in to the skin until fully absorbed. In the evening, apply a few drops of the serum directly on to cleansed, dry skin. Gently massage in to the skin until fully absorbed and leave on overnight. Shake well before use. Safety Warning Avoid contact with eyes. See more",
